metadata.name: 0 - The Fool
metadata.description:
The Fool is all about new beginnings. This card represents a time of innocence and naivete, when you are ready to take on the world with fresh eyes. The Fool is all about taking risks and embracing the unknown, and reminds us that sometimes the best path in life is the one less traveled.  
	
Upright: Beginnings, Innocence, Leap of Faith, Originality, Spontaneity

Reversed: Chaos, Folly, Lack of Direction, Naivety, Poor Judgement, Stupidity
